## Superseded from submodule-worktree-permission-retry-pattern

```yaml
name: submodule-worktree-permission-retry-pattern
category: tooling
date: 2026-05-07
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-local
tags: [myrmidon, swarm, worktree, submodule, permission, retry, git, force-with-lease, agent-dispatch]
```

Sub-agents dispatched into a git submodule worktree hit transient "permission denied"
on the first git call due to lazy git-dir path-allowlist cache resolution. Fix: embed
retry-5x + 3s sleep guidance verbatim in the dispatch prompt. Orchestrator stale-lease
recovery: `git ls-remote` to read live remote tip, pass to `--force-with-lease=<branch>:<sha>`.
Verified: Odysseus → Myrmidons session 2026-05-07; 3 sub-agents recovered (PRs #505,
#595, #649).

---

## Superseded from worktree-agent-plan-mode-avoidance

```yaml
name: worktree-agent-plan-mode-avoidance
category: tooling
date: 2026-04-12
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-local
tags: [worktree, agent, plan-mode, execution, myrmidon, haiku]
```

Prevent worktree-isolated agents from stopping to plan: use Haiku model for mechanical
tasks, imperative-only numbered `Run:` prompt (no section headers). Detection: output
has plan summary but no PR URL. SendMessage is not available for worktree agents after
return — must relaunch. Verified: 26 PRs created in ProjectOdyssey without manual
intervention (Wave D/E, 2026-04-12).

