## Superseded from worktree-migration-testing-patterns

```yaml
name: worktree-migration-testing-patterns
category: tooling
date: 2026-03-28
version: "1.0.0"
verification: unverified
tags: [worktree, migration, clone-to-worktree, integration-tests, idempotency, auto-merge]
```

Two related patterns: (1) migrate clone-based workflows (rm -rf teardown) to git worktree
lifecycle; (2) write integration tests against real committed SKILL.md files. Worktree
pattern: `git worktree add /tmp/... -b <branch> origin/main` → work → `git worktree remove`
+ `git worktree prune`. Integration test: 6-test checklist (fixture exists, before-condition,
modified=True, condition removed, round-trip, idempotent). Verified: ProjectMnemosyne PR
#991, integration tests for fix_remaining_warnings.py.
